      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>VADAY-Gilad. July 27, 2000. His friends at Bigfoot mourn his loss. His untimely passing has left a void in our hearts that will not soon be refilled. Our sincere condolences go out to his family and to all who knew him. We were all blessed for having him in our lives and will remain so for having him in our thoughts. His friends and family at Bigfoot</p>
